ECABEV — Enhanced Channel Attention BEV
=======================================

This repository is the official implementation of:

    Argho Dey, Yunfei Yin, Zheng Yuan, Zhiwen Zeng, Xianjian Bao, Md Minhazul Islam.
    "Enhanced BEV Scene Segmentation: De-Noise Channel Attention for
     Resource-Constrained Environments."
    Computers, Materials & Continua, 2025/2026.
    DOI: 10.32604/cmc.2025.074122

ECABEV builds upon the BEVCar codebase and extends it with three novel
contributions (de-noise enhanced channel attention, bilinear interpolation
layer normalization, and a scalable cross-entropy BEV loss).

